metadata.name: Matrixport
metadata.description: NexusBTC (“NBTC”) is a wrapped Bitcoin token by Matrixport designed to facilitate cross-chain transactions within the DeFI ecosystem such as with babypiexyz.io or pumpbtc.xyz. The token is backed by a reserve of Bitcoin that exceeds a 1:1 ratio. This over-collateralization provides additional security and stability for users.

metadata.name: enzoBTC
metadata.description: enzoBTC is a wrapped Bitcoin token by Lorenzo protocol designed to facilitate cross-chain transactions within the DeFI ecosystem.
